import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { FeedlistService } from './feedlist.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-feedlist', templateUrl: './feedlist.component.html', styleUrls: ['./feedlist.component.scss'] }) export class FeedlistComponent { likedToggle:boolean = false feeds : any; constructor(private router:Router,private feedlistservice:FeedlistService){} ngOn fatchFeed(){ this.feedlistservice.getFeeds().subscribe((res:any)=>{ console.log(res) this.feeds = res['feeds'] }) } likedPost(event:any){ console.log(event) this.likedToggle = !this.likedToggle let userId = localStorage.getItem('userId') let postId = event let data = {userId : userId , postId : postId} this.feedlistservice.likedDislikePost(data).subscribe((res:any)=>{ console.log(res) }) } }
